<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV28">
<l>paṭaittapāri ṭantaḷanta tuṇṭumiḻntu pauvanīr</l>
<l>paṭaittaṭaitta tiṟkiṭantu muṉkaṭainta peṟṟiyōy</l>
<l>miṭaittamāli mālimāṉvi laṅkukāla ṉūrpukap</l>
<l>paṭaikkalamvi ṭuttapalpa ṭaittaṭakkai māyaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You with the greatness of digging out the earth [that You] created, measuring,</l>
<l rend="indent">Swallowing, and spitting it out,</l>
<l>[and] of creating the watery ocean, blocking [it to build a bridge], lying upon it,</l>
<l rend="indent">and churning [it] previously!</l>
<l>O wonderful Lord whose broad arms with many weapons dispatch missiles,</l>
<l>In such a way that Māli full [of anger] and animal[-like] [Su]māli enter Yama’s town!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
